[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    458[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Standard output safety primitives]                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    459[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scope filter (no diagnosis; no treatment             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    460[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      adjustment; no controlled-substance handling; no     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    461[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      legally-binding eligibility determinations; no       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    462[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      complex-appeal preparation)                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    463[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Vendor-managed guardrail layer                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    464[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    465[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Care-coordination-specific verification]               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    466[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Every system-of-record claim grounded in retrieved   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    467[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      data with source identifier                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    468[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Every proposed action authorized for the patient at  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    469[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      this scope (appointment scheduling allowed for this  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    470[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      appointment type; refill-request allowed for this    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    471[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      medication class; care-team-message-compose allowed  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    472[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      for this care-team role)                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    473[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Every benefits or eligibility statement carries the  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    474[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      institutional disclaimer template                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    475[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Every prior-auth or appeal handling routed to case   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    476[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      manager appropriately                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    477[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Every emergency or crisis indicator honored          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    478[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Disclosure language present where required           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    479[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    480[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    481[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: response cleared for delivery, replaced with   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    482[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    a safer template, or regenerated with corrections]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    483[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    484[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
