[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    486[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ACTION EXECUTION + IDEMPOTENT WRITES ──────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    487[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    488[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Where the conversation produced a system-write         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    489[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    decision (schedule appointment, submit refill, place   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    490[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    referral followup, log SDoH screen, route case manager │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    491[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    handoff, file mandatory report)]                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    492[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    493[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Idempotent write pattern]                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    494[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Generate idempotency_key per action                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    495[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Submit write to system of record with idempotency    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    496[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      key                                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    497[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Confirm write acknowledged                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    498[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Update open-item state with new evidence             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    499[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Capture system-of-record-returned identifiers in     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    500[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      audit trail                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    501[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    502[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Failure handling]                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    503[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Transient failures: retry with backoff               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    504[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Persistent failures: escalate to case manager with   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    505[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      context; mark item state as "blocked" with reason    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    506[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Race conditions: idempotency key ensures no          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    507[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      duplicate writes                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    508[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    509[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    510[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: confirmed system-of-record write or escalation │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    511[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    event for case-manager handling]                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    512[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    513[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    514[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    515[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── WARM HANDOFF + ESCALATION ROUTING ─────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    516[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    517[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Warm-handoff triggers]                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    518[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Emergency screen positive (911 for medical;          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    519[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      988 for suicide; institutional crisis line)          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    520[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient explicitly requests human                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    521[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Out-of-scope question (clinical, complex benefits,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    522[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      complex SDoH, complex appeal)                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    523[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sensitive disclosure pattern detected (IPV, child    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    524[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      abuse, elder abuse, severe SDoH crisis)              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    525[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Mandatory-reporting trigger                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    526[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot confidence below threshold                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    527[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Persistent failure to close an open item             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    528[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient frustration signal                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    529[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sustained pattern of concern (repeated missed        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    530[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      appointments, repeated incomplete referrals,         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    531[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      repeated declined outreach)                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    532[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    533[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Handoff targets]                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    534[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active emergency: 911 with stay-on-the-line guidance │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    535[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Suicidal crisis: 988 plus institutional crisis line  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    536[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      plus mental-health-bot warm handoff where applicable │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    537[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Clinical question: patient's PCP or specialist       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    538[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      message (with patient review and approval)           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    539[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-coordination escalation: case manager with      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    540[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conversation context attached                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    541[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Benefits-escalation: plan benefits counselor         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    542[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pharmacy-escalation: pharmacist                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    543[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - SDoH-escalation: care-management or community health │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    544[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      worker                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    545[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Mandatory-reporting disclosure: licensed clinician   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    546[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (mandatory reporter) with conversation context       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    547[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    548[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Warm-handoff payload]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    549[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent conversation transcript                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    550[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active conditions and medications (where consented)  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    551[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Open-item state                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    552[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent encounters and pending appointments           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    553[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Trigger reason and screening result where applicable │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    554[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient's preferred contact method                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    555[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient's stated preferences                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    556[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot's structured summary                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    557[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    558[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Bridge-and-stay pattern]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    559[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot bridges to human within the platform             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    560[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot stays present until human has joined             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    561[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient does not start over                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    562[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    563[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    564[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: handoff event with structured payload to       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    565[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    appropriate target, conversation continuity preserved] │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    566[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
