[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    582[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Every system-of-record write recorded with returned  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    583[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      identifiers                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    584[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Every escalation recorded with target and outcome    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    585[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
