[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    596[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-experience scores (CAHPS-style or            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    597[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      bot-specific)                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    598[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Case-manager-productivity metrics                    │
