[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    600[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      condition, age cohort, sex, social-determinant       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    601[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      flags, plan-cohort, geography)                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    602[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    603[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Outcome correlation as long-time-horizon commitment]   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    604[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-gap-closure rate (HEDIS-style measures where    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    605[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      applicable)                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    606[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Hospitalization rate                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    607[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - ED-visit rate                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    608[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Readmission rate                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    609[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Total-cost-of-care trajectory (where the deployer    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    610[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      bears risk)                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    611[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-reported-outcomes trajectory                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    612[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Multi-quarter to multi-year implementation           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    613[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Owned jointly by care-management leadership,         │
